# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

_DISPLAY_FRAME_ - Display (optionally) the current frame image

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 _DISPLAY_FRAME_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primtive asks the display system to display the current frame.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

Should be replaced by a call to the general ORAC-DR implementation.

